@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token =
@tenantId =

### 获取 CSRF Token（写接口前执行）
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 获取可视化总览（需要权限: visualization:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取流程列表（需要权限: visualization:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/processes?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取实例列表（需要权限: visualization:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/instances?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取指标（需要权限: visualization:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取审计数据（需要权限: visualization:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/audit?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 保存可视化流程（需要权限: visualization:process:save）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/processes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "示例流程",
  "nodes": [],
  "edges": []
}

### 更新可视化流程（需要权限: visualization:process:update）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/processes/{processId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processId": "{processId}",
  "name": "示例流程-v2",
  "nodes": [],
  "edges": []
}

### 发布可视化流程（需要权限: visualization:process:publish）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/visualization/processes/{processId}/publication
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "发布测试"
}
